quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"Toto balia abakhaya ni nashilalasa khubo, obekanyilisie nohomba olabekanyilisia tawe, shibalisuubila tawe."
  2,7,"Nyasaye yasuba khumioyo chiabu nende khutsimbulililo tsiabu, ne tsindolelo tsiabu tsilikhwo shiokhutsifunikha, mana bali nende eshinyasio eshikhongo."
  2,8,"Ne mubandu balio baboolanga mbu, “Khwasuubila mu Nyasaye nende Inyanga ya Indukho.” ne shibali abasuubili tawe."
  2,9,"Benyanga okhukatia Nyasaye nende Abasuubili, ne shibakatinjia halali abeene butswa, ne shibamanyilekho tawe."
  2,10,"Emioyo chiabu chilimwo obulwale, mana Nyasaye nabameta obulwale. Ne bali nende eshinyasio eshilulu khukalia ka bakaatinjia."
  2,11,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu, "Mulakhole obwononi khushialo tawe." nabo baboola mbu, "Khubwatoto efwe nefwe khukaasinjia amakhuwa okhuba amalayi.”"
  2,12,"Koo, toto bo nibo abononi, halali shibamanyile tawe."
  2,13,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu, “Suubile shinga Abandu (Omurumwa nende abaloondi bebe) basuubila.” nibaboola mbu, “Khusuubile shinga abasilu basuubila?” Koo, toto bo nibo abasilu, halali shibamanyile tawe."
  2,14,"Ne nibabukana nende abasuubili, nibaboola mbu, “Khwasuubila.” Ne nibatong'a bo nende amashetani kabu, nibaboola mbu, “Toto efwe khuli ninenyu. Toto efwe khukholanga butswa omubayo.""
  2,15,"Nyasaye yalababayila omubayo, ne yalabalekha mubukori bwabu nibayiyayiyanga mubuwofu."
  2,16,"Abo nibo bakula obukori khubulunjifu, mana inganga yabu niilanyola obukhala tawe, mana nibalaba abalunjifu tawe."